Tim McGraw is set to raise money for a gun control charity in Connecticut .
The 47-year-old singer is scheduled to perform a benefit concert for the Sandy Hook Promise group on July 17 .
Critics have said that McGraw risks losing his career the same way female country trio the Dixie Chicks never bounced back from criticizing President George W Bush .
McGraw's opening act Bill Currington walked away from the project after the backlash .